unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start()

	-- Kill NPC
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_KILLER) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(ID_KILLER) then
		Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(ID_KILLER, AISTATE_TAUNT_LOOP)
		Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(ID_KILLER, 0, true)
		Hydra.ActorInterruptPrimaryPower(ID_KILLER)
		Hydra.QActorPower(ID_KILLER, POWER_KILL, ID_NPC)
	
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_KILLER)
	end
	-- NPC Dies
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(ID_NPC, ID_BLEED)
	Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(ID_NPC)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_NPC, false)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_BLOOD_LOC, EG_BLOOD)
	Hydra.RemoveBuffs(ID_NPC, AISMP_OPT_OUT, "AISMP_OptOutBuff")
	
	-- Enable Killer normal AI
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_KILLER) and Hydra.ActorIsAlive(ID_KILLER) then
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(ID_KILLER, true)
	end
	
end

unk_993f312.value:
-- Killer setup
Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(ID_KILLER, AISTATE_TAUNT_LOOP, ID_KILLER, 0)
Hydra.ActorOverrideAIAwarenessRadius(ID_KILLER, 2, true)

-- NPC setup
Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_NPC, true)
Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_NPC, ANIMSET_OVERRIDE)
Hydra.QActorAnimLoop(ID_NPC, ANIMKEY_NEUTRAL_ALT, 0)
Hydra.ActorSetBloody(ID_NPC, 1)
ID_BLEED = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_NPC, EG_BLEED, true)
Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(AISMP_OPT_OUT, "AISMP_OptOutBuff", ID_NPC)

-- VFX Setup
Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_BLOOD_LOC, 4)
